<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0791b08" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0791b08">即空不斷悟避境趍寂之非乘大乘智得如來法身不但證假涅槃<choice cb:resp="#resp1"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>也</note>
<note n="0791b11" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0791b11"><choice cb:resp="#resp1"><corr>福</corr><sic>禍</sic></choice>慧具足即成佛亦所應得何況止於不離佛耶</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0789b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0789b02">一大事言西方起故為一大事故耳一大事者度眾生出生死海也</note>
<note n="0790b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b01">往來獄門喻釋迦長伺獄外喻彌陀佛</note>
<note n="0790b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b02">因以飢寒而死曰瘦</note>
<note n="0790b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b03">此言西方起教由彌陀之宿因深也凡一切事皆有因有願有行但不依自性起不得為正故必見法身始名正因依自性發願始名正願依自性修習始名正行彌陀有此三者是其宿因既深故起教亦大也</note>
<note n="0790b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b04">人知果德屬於自身而不知由度生方能成果則西方起故正表彌陀之果德也．此段對下依因性看非對上宿因深說</note>
<note n="0790b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b05">人知往生在于念行而不知因淨性方名攝受則西方起故惟依眾生之自性</note>
<note n="0790b06" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b06">此言佛說西方勝境者謂眾生所欲在是故順其情耳</note>
<note n="0790b07" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b07">向非情量云者意謂說王宮珍異亦就彼情量言之耳若極言其微妙則非田舍兒情量所及矣</note>
<note n="0790b08" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0790b08">此言世尊以西方訓化者為眾生穢相本空故易為<g ref="#CB18949">󴨅</g>耳</note>
<note n="0791b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b01">說淨土時又移其悅色營官嗜利者而欣淨土也</note>
<note n="0791b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b02">前言依因性者言由眾生性體之清淨非關行願與念力也此言勝方便者言由眾生性力之殊勝非關自力與他力也</note>
<note n="0791b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b03">世尊說十念功成者為眾生自性本具原有如是最勝之方便耳</note>
<note n="0791b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b04">上七段言度眾生以下言導二乘教菩薩．此言二乘必修淨土然後得證真理不墮於斷滅是故如來教生極樂令入大乘</note>
<note n="0791b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b05">一者無明四段正申言乘得如來法身受業惑苦</note>
<note n="0791b06" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b06">無漏業雖與有漏業異然畢竟亦是業因有微細之虛妄故起此業如二乘之躭寂滅菩薩之欲度生皆是</note>
<note n="0791b07" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b07">斷續流滅言其變易生死之不絕</note>
<note n="0791b08" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b08">即空不斷悟避境趍寂之非乘大乘智得如來法身不但證假涅槃巳也</note>
<note n="0791b09" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b09">此言菩薩常樂念佛故世世值佛不沒于煩惱所以世尊指歸彌陀以堅忍力堅忍者親近彌陀正以堅自心之忍力使不退轉</note>
<note n="0791b10" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b10">異處行者不與佛同居也</note>
<note n="0791b11" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b11">禍慧具足即成佛亦所應得何況止於不離佛耶</note>
<note n="0791b12" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0791b12">於一切眾生不循理道事我心忍耐不為計校且慈力教訓之名生忍於境緣之法有難堪難禁處亦忍耐不行名法忍</note>
<note n="0792b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0792b01">上說菩薩念佛已竟下復引天如云云者恐人疑禪宗悟道之後不必念佛往生故引此破之亦足明龍樹未盡之意耳</note>
<note n="0792b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0792b02">政言密密修淨土也</note>
<note n="0792b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0792b03">總結龍樹天如以應前堅忍之題</note>
</p>
